          "html": "<div><b>Betweenness Centrality&nbsp;</b><br></div><div>- the number of paths between between $s \\to t$ without $v$ / number of shortest paths from $s \\to t$</div><div><br></div><div><b>Katz Centrality</b></div><div>- the number of walks from $s \\to t$ where each link in the walk is weighted $\\alpha$</div><div><br></div><div><b>PageRank centrality&nbsp;</b></div><div>- the probability of walking from $s \\to t$ where each link in the walk is weighted by $\\alpha P_{ij}$&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\">… and more! communicability, etc. …&nbsp;</div>",
          "position": {
            "x": 67,
            "y": 233,
            "width": 1760,
            "height": 800
          },
          "linkId": "6ff818c2-01dd-4eef-b252-14ca580fa52e",
          "syncId": "6ff818c2-01dd-4eef-b252-14ca580fa52e"
        },
        {
          "id": "0f30f827-3011-4b6d-9347-f939135d31ed",
          "type": "text",
          "preset": "title",
          "html": "<span style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em;\">Path and Walk Counting is central to&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 5.76px; text-transform: uppercase;\">…</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;\">&nbsp;Centrality! </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 5.76px; text-transform: uppercase;\">…</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;\">&nbsp;</span></span>",
          "position": {
            "x": 61,
            "y": 51,
            "width": 1807,
            "height": 200
          },
